rent story! </strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>STORY 2: Learn a hard lesson while attending to a desperate housewife alongside your loyal girlfriend...</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>STORY 3: You just found out your JAV crush is working at Japan's biggest nightclub, what are you waiting for?</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3893500/extras/78b66a9171b7e75f1faf00f057236444.poster.avif?t=1756978766\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3893500/extras/78b66a9171b7e75f1faf00f057236444.webm?t=1756978766\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3893500/extras/78b66a9171b7e75f1faf00f057236444.mp4?t=1756978766\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3893500/extras/e84c38d0d158ffa57c92c1834f873ea4.poster.avif?t=1756978766\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3893500/extras/e84c38d0d158ffa57c92c1834f873ea4.webm?t=1756978766\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3893500/extras/e84c38d0d158ffa57c92c1834f873ea4.mp4?t=1756978766\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3893500/extras/e3ea2b8b99bb84b2713122ef1c8299d6.poster.avif?t=1756978766\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3893500/extras/e3ea2b8b99bb84b271312